Invocation Name: amazing food
des:
We’re a partnership of Northern Ireland food and drink businesses working together to access valuable online foodie and drink related online traffic. Why? To showcase our brands together in ways designed to truly bring products to life.
Using great blog content, exclusive interviews and video content, we’ll make customers a part of the local food and drink world. Our goal…working as business owners to turn customers into a community of brand advocates. This is a unique opportunity to be part of a new food and drink community online. To mould a passionate community around your brands.
